originalText.text: Allie is the most professional and nice man ever. Cannot recommend enough this business. Super punctual and responsible! His services and products for rats, bedbugs and fleas were incredibly effective and also very quick. Lifesaver!

originalText.text: Amazing service! Cannot recommend highly enough. I had a major roach problem in my apartment - I used to dread even entering my kitchen at night due to how bad it was. As of now, however, it's been about five weeks since my place was treated and I can't even remember the last time I've seen a single roach. It's night and day. The business is very responsive, courteous, professional, affordable, and above all, effective. Definitely use them if you have a pest problem!

originalText.text: I had no idea what to do about a tiny mouse in the tiny Soho apartment that my girlfriend was freaking out over. I called at 9am and he was there at 11am.  Full service, professional, guaranteed and said call back if any problem and I will take care of it. Highly recommend. The price is right.

originalText.text: These guys are the TOPS. My cat chased a rat into my bedroom at 3am. I must have called every so-called “24 hr” exterminator in NYC, and Ali and his team were the only ones who really had a team available, and were even there 10 minutes after the call. 5 minutes later, no more rat. Thank you All-City! Total life savers and good guys.
